<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ذ هـ ب:</span> <span class="c2">(الذَّهَبُ)</span> مَعْدِنٌ ثَمِينٌ وَشَيْءٌ <span class="c2">(مُذَهَّبٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(مُذْهَبٌ)</span> أَيْ مُمَوَّهٌ بِالذَّهَبِ. وَ <span class="c2">(ذَهَبَ)</span> يَذْهَبُ <span class="c2">(ذَهَابًا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(ذُهُوبًا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(مَذْهَبًا)</span> بِفَتْحِ الْمِيمِ أَيْ مَرَّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>